BESA.Kernel.Agent

Class BehaviorBESA

  • java.lang.Object
    • BESA.Kernel.Agent.BehaviorBESA
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProtocolBehavior

    public class BehaviorBESA
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This class represents a behavior of a BESA agent, to which a series of guards is associated.
    Since:
    JDK1.0
